body: An interactive (if html checkboxes count) incubator checklist for checking if release comply with ASF policy. A simple Asciidoctor example that produces a webpage rather than slides.

title: Navigating the ASF incubation process
body: Initial version of slides converted to asciidocs. This talk (in several slightly different forms) was given to several large companies in China in late 2018 want to know more about the ASF and the Apache Way. The expected length of the presentation is 45 minutes, but extra material is included for a longer talk if needed.
